e47","tid":1223070,"uid":48057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"piah"},{"pid":"40605ad11e659752ac512268176ed017da145d41","tid":1223070,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7c00e70550ddbfd226a83beecac8636bd10bf3","tid":1223070,"uid":228195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"我琴日係銅鑼灣希慎附近既地鋪<br />\n見到入面嘅幾位女sales都著黑色自由閪T shirt支持<br />\n我有停低拍手掌多謝佢地<br />\n有無巴絲記得係邊間鋪頭？<br />\n無印象係咪恩平道"},{"pid":"f5f3e631309bf21cabdfe49b434e668d44b20f8d","tid":1223070,"uid":162046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7bb1976cace68ef8981793af402f8ab8878e0ba","tid":1223070,"uid":258373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:09:07.000Z","msg":"Push. Let the people know that good deed is rewarded (not a must, but it&rsquo;s nice)"},{"pid":"e363d5908785d3c52ebc5ec3ab3b922eece1cada","tid":1223070,"uid":95097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:17:13.000Z","msg":"不如整個google map?"},{"pid":"a148f4dbfeedcdbb53c516977b751e18313cc12b","tid":1223070,"uid":23944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e607ae919220f1b1fba92646cf67980aaba97f74","tid":1223070,"uid":15230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:22:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我朋友用Google Map整合咗香港一啲公開表態反送中、罷市、甚至提供物資比群眾嘅企業同商舖。<br />\n呢啲商舖可能係你屋企同工作地點附近，希望大家多多支持同幫襯呢啲商舖，向佢地致敬同打氣。相信呢個係每一個香港人都可以做到嘅。<br />\n我哋亦希望透過咁樣鼓勵更多商舖參與和支持呢一場民眾抗爭，話俾呢個無能嘅政府知，香港人上下一心，企喺同一陣線！</span><br />\n<br />\n地圖：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2F5dhCU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2F5dhCU&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8GVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=8235055e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2F5dhCU</a><br />\n<br />\n提出修改或新增店鋪資料：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/skA3mAyExNsooAMZ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FskA3mAyExNsooAMZ8&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8GVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=26825f85\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/skA3mAyExNsooAMZ8</a><br />\n<br />\n主要Source: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2R9gTIM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2R9gTIM&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8GVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=133a68ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2R9gTIM</a>， 香港01，社交媒體"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"巴打，我本身都諗住整一個良心地圖， <br />\n好多謝你同你朋友已經行動咗。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要人罷買黑心店，都要有代替品。 <br />\n所以好好幫良心店宣傳，互相支持都好重要！ <br />\n香港人幫香港人！  <br />\n<br />\n既然巴打同朋友已經整咗個地圖， <br />\n有無諗過幫佢地進一步宣傳？<br />\n 例如親身去，影相，拍片，食評，whatever。<br />\n<br />\n可以加入去地圖又好，開個fb/ig push又好。<br />\n<br />\n如果你有興趣咁做，tg me.  <br />\n利申：影相拍片JJ<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec60ceeb1810fb58367102dbaf329f2580f06470","tid":1223070,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:56:22.000Z","msg":"福利模型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不枉我幫襯左你廿幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14d9f89369082fbf69622d2f2ade6d6b1db75ef","tid":1223070,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"驚唔驚比人抽後算帳呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35689d42d36ad213b68c04ad6cf9bda9921e5847","tid":1223070,"uid":15230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"push 比更多人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2a317757abab380c7d44f52ff737cc0080f6a0","tid":1223070,"uid":23944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14d9f89369082fbf69622d2f2ade6d6b1db75ef","tid":1223070,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"驚唔驚比人抽後算帳呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"我都有諗個呢個問題，<br />\n但我覺得佢地表得態多數都唔驚<br />\n怕秋後算帳嘅話，咁我地更加要支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4d6f22d6b31a9d2587ddbc1c7b60ce709d0fe1","tid":1223070,"uid":75735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>芳雅居 Fang Nga Place</ins></strong></span><br />\n琴日好多手足都係炮台山食完飯先去<br />\n相信好都人都會知道依間花店<br />\n朝早已經係門口放左好多籃白花<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">免費派發 每人可拎1支</span></strong><br />\n我同朋友見到 唔想拎著數<br />\n諗住食完飯番去比錢買<br />\n去到老闆話白色花已經派曬啦 就算比錢買都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記得多多支持<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpeRct0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpeRct0.png&h=2b813e1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>好景文具</ins></strong></span> <br />\n都係炮台山 係上面間花店附近<br />\n我同friend諗住去買Card Board舉<br />\n老闆見我地黑衫黑褲即刻話唔駛錢送比我地<br />\n仲叫我地要加油<br />\n我地梗係唔好意思 最後都有比錢<br />\n老闆真係好nice好溫暖<br />\n又係記得多多支持<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkphSvw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkphSvw.png&h=26a1659d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03516300e134377353749b85f369c7d1c74bbb0f","tid":1223070,"uid":73248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:24:49.000Z","msg":"花墟有冇邊間花店係反送中？"},{"pid":"f2a54074895be0bbb02343a7b79395ff58f3babb","tid":1223070,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:32:46.000Z",